author: MiniWarGaming
description:
In this special narrative campaign Matthew and Luka are joined by two guests (Mark and David) to play through a campaign where the board is destructible, and evolves throughout the entire campaign!  The Orks and Tyranids are fighting over the remains of an Imperial planet.  Who will be the victor?
